WEBVTT

00:02:27.946 --> 00:02:30.291
seven had already been taken hostage.

00:02:30.291 --> 00:02:32.078
So we were careful.

00:02:32.078 --> 00:02:36.152
We were using armored 
vehicles, decoy cars,

00:02:36.152 --> 00:02:39.207
changing patterns of travel,
changing homes,

00:02:39.207 --> 00:02:41.998
all sorts of security measures.

00:02:43.258 --> 00:02:49.208
Yet on a cold winter night
of January '98, it was my turn.

00:02:49.208 --> 00:02:53.185
When I entered my flat
in Vladikavkaz with a guard,

00:02:53.185 --> 00:02:55.341
we were surrounded by armed men.

00:02:56.781 --> 00:02:58.998
They took the guard,
they put him on the floor,

00:02:58.998 --> 00:03:01.622
they beat him up in front of me,